properties.documentation:
A job poster with administrator privileges
Responsibilities:
 Job Poster Functionalities  Manage Advertisement  Manage sponsors  Send email notification  Manage Website Content

A user who is registered with the website and hold a username and password
Responsibilities:
 Browse Website  Search Jobs  Login  Logout

A job poster who is registered as an employer to the website
Responsibilities:
 Job Poster Functionalities  Manage employer profile  Search candidates for a job requirement

Advertisement service by Google Responsibilities :  
  • Provide publish ready advertisements

Email service by Google Responsibilities:  
  • Manage an email account for all notification sent via email

A website user who can post jobs on the website
Responsibilities:
 Authorized User Functionalities  Post a job

A website user who has a profile of a job seeker
Responsibilities :
 Authorized User functionalities  Manage Subscriptions  Manage Job-Seeker Profile

Any general internet user who comes on the website
Responsibilities:  Browse the website  Search job opportunities  Subscribe to email notification  Register on the website with a specific role
